<h2>Install</h2>

<p>This layout mode is not included in <a href="../isotope.pkgd.js">isotope.pkgd.js</a> and must be installed separately.</p>

<p><code>horiz</code> layout mode was previously named <code>horizontal</code> in Isotope v2.</p>

<p><a href="https://raw.github.com/metafizzy/isotope-horizontal/master/horizontal.js">Download horizontal.js on GitHub</a>.</p>

<p>Install with Bower:</p>

``` bash
bower install isotope-horizontal
```

<p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/isotope-horizontal">Install with npm</a>:</p>

``` bash
npm install isotope-horizontal
```

