<h2>Options</h2>

{{! --------------------------------------------------- }}

<h3>verticalAlignment</h3>

<p>Aligns items vertically. Set as a decimal <code>0</code> to <code>1</code>.</p>

``` js
/* default
horiz: {
  // align to origin edge
  verticalAlignment: 0
} */

horiz: {
  // align to center
  verticalAlignment: 0.5
}

horiz: {
  // align to opposite edge
  verticalAlignment: 1
}
```

